OL,3,CHow is this pub highlighting wealth
OL,4,Cinequality?
OL,6,FA London pub is charging customers
OL,7,Fbased on how much they earn.
OL,9,FThe Fair Pour, in Holborn, is opening
OL,10,Fits doors for the first and last time
OL,11,Fto offer customers a way to tackle
OL,12,Fwealth inequality by paying or their
OL,13,Fpints based on what they earn for one
OL,14,Fday only.
OL,16,FOxfam have taken over the Old Queen's
OL,17,FHead serving non-alcoholic drinks from
OL,18,Fmidday until 9pm and all proceeds will
OL,19,Fbe going to the charity.
