OL,3,CHow is this pub highlighting wealth
OL,4,Cinequality?
OL,6,F"The minimum is #3.00 but we paid #5
OL,7,Feach," said one group.
OL,9,F"My colleagues put it on the group
OL,10,Fchat and any chance to give to charity
OL,11,Fis a nice thing to do...everybody is
OL,12,Ffeeling the squeeze even people who
OL,13,Fwould previously be on a good salary,
OL,14,Fthey're having to not spend as much
OL,15,Fmoney on drinks or nights out but also
OL,16,Fbuying groceries and things like that,
OL,17,Feverything is just so much more."
OL,19,FAnother added: "We wanted to come
OL,20,Fdown, and see what it's about - any
OL,21,Freason to give to a good cause."
