OL,3,CHow is this pub highlighting wealth
OL,4,Cinequality?
OL,6,FThe pop up aims to highlight the
OL,7,Fgrowing wealth inequality in the world
OL,8,Fas they say income inequalities within
OL,9,Fcountries is worsening. It is taking
OL,10,Fplace during the Davos World Economic
OL,11,FForum.
OL,13,FThe charity add that "this unique
OL,14,Festablishment challenges the status
OL,15,Fquo with a pricing system that
OL,16,Freflects the stark reality of wealth
OL,17,Fdisparity".
