OL,6,FAnother customer said: "The Fair Pour
OL,7,Fpub I just thought it was a really
OL,8,Fcreative idea - I really liked the
OL,9,Fidea."
OL,11,FThe drinks on offer were; Nepobaby
OL,12,FBitter, Super Rich Stout,
OL,13,FBillionaire's Brew and Rich List Lager
OL,14,Fand cocktails including Old Money
OL,15,FFashioned, Highballer, The
OL,16,FBillionaire's Breeze and Caviar
OL,17,FCollins will be available.
