OL,3,CHow is this pub highlighting wealth
OL,4,Cinequality?
OL,6,FThe names have been inspired by words
OL,7,Fassociated with the wealth gap, which
OL,8,Fwas the main inspiration behind
OL,9,Ftoday's event.
OL,11,FAnna Marriott, Inequality Policy lead
OL,12,Ffor Oxfam : "We do campaigning events
OL,13,Flike this all over the world at this
OL,14,Ftime of year..to encourage that
OL,15,Fbroader conversation.
OL,17,F"London of course is the capital of
OL,18,Fthe UK, it's where our government sits
OL,19,Fand the city of London is where a lot
OL,20,Fof the billionaires make their money."
